# Testing Backend (Python)

Incluye **`app/`** y **`scripts/`**. Índice global: `testing-strategy.mdc`.

## Stack

pytest + pytest-asyncio + pytest-cov (**≥80%**), httpx AsyncClient, mongomock, pytest-mock.

## Estructura

```
backend/tests/
├── conftest.py
├── unit/          # services, agents, rag, repositories, models
├── integration/   # api routes, orchestrator
├── scripts/       # seed_data, index_policies, batch_evaluations
└── smoke/         # deployed API (skip sin SMOKE_TEST_URL)
```

## Reglas

1. Toda función pública en `app/` → test unitario
2. Todo endpoint → test integration
3. Todo script → test en `tests/scripts/` (mock DB + vector store)
4. Mock siempre: LLM, AI Search, Tavily
5. Nombrar: `test_<comportamiento>_when_<condición>`

## Comandos

```bash
cd backend && pytest --cov=app --cov=scripts --cov-fail-under=80
ruff check . && mypy app
```
